00:20:07,267 --> 00:20:08,709
Woke up perfectly refreshed.

207
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:10,972
So that tells you something.

208
00:20:11,933 --> 00:20:13,036
So that's not an aim.

209
00:20:13,316 --> 00:20:15,659
That's not an aim in order to become fully liberated.

210
00:20:15,778 --> 00:20:19,605
I'm just saying that's a consequence.

211
00:20:19,625 --> 00:20:21,067
And in maintaining silence.

