00:21:33,414 --> 00:21:55,086
loathing them and it is as if a woman or man when young or delicate and fond of dressing up having washed their hair would be troubled ashamed and full of loathing because they had the corpse of a snake or of a dog or of a man hung around their neck so these bhikkhus

228
00:21:55,538 --> 00:22:06,536
being troubled by their own bodies, ashamed of them and loathing them, by themselves, deprived themselves of life and deprived each other of life.

