00:24:57,011 --> 00:25:04,220
Looking at a tooth in your mind might bring up a certain, I don't know, skin, unless it's old and wrinkled and horrible.

257
00:25:06,462 --> 00:25:10,768
Flesh, sinews, bones, bone marrow, kidneys.

258
00:25:12,109 --> 00:25:17,276
So when you go through the list for yourself, you see, you're actually just trying to catch your relationship to it.

259
00:25:17,997 --> 00:25:21,580
Heart, liver, spleen, lungs.

260
00:25:22,321 --> 00:25:24,084
I mean, I don't know what my spleen looks like even.

