00:25:27,151 --> 00:25:53,022
intestines undigested food excrement bile now this is more like it bile phlegm pus blood sweat and fat now when you when you get in contact with your image or when you get in contact with with that even in ordinary daily lives as we were talking about going to going to the toilet uh just catch you know your relationship to because you ask yourself is it necessary

