00:31:11,282 --> 00:31:37,375
so any excuse you know but i was very relieved to read that in fact the buddha doesn't say this either in the discourses and the people who put the abhidhamma together don't say it either and i think the reason is that the base of the of the of the mind is the whole body is the whole body the mind so any any information that comes in from the five senses

