00:44:53,398 --> 00:45:01,990
That when we're actually looking at the body, it's all our contemplation, a lot of our contemplation is in the body.

478
00:45:02,291 --> 00:45:06,518
It's the breathing, the posture, the full awareness of what we're doing all the time.

479
00:45:07,119 --> 00:45:10,443
And then there's that whole business of a relationship to the body.

480
00:45:10,824 --> 00:45:20,958
